INTELLECTUAL PROPERTY NOTICE

The following constitute proprietary intellectual property of Auracelle AI Governance Labs
and are protected under applicable intellectual property law:

  - The E-IAIG-HT (Enhanced Intent–Autonomy–Interaction–Governance — Hierarchical Theory)
    framework, including its mathematical architecture, equations, and weighting methodology
  - The g-GWC (General Governance Wargaming Capacity) metric and its computation methodology
  - The BGC (Base Governance Capacity) domain taxonomy and scoring architecture
  - The NOF (Normalized Operational Factor) library, including all CD-NOFs
  - The Governance_Gap() metric and seam identification methodology
  - The Stratum I / II / III hierarchical architecture
  - The Cognitive Domain (CD) stratum specification, sub-domains, and NOF library
  - The gray zone governance analytical framing as applied to Arctic High North wargaming
  - The KPI/CSF framework and success criteria architecture for SAS-219

